videos.description: Matthew Hurt drives to the basket and draws contact as he contorts in the air to get the and-1 layup to fall in off the glass.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Duke's Hurt contorts to make and-1 lay-in) 2020/03/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Duke's Hurt contorts to make and-1 lay-in

videos.description: David Robinson lets out a laugh as his son, Justin Robinson, shoots from deep and gets a fortuitous bounce off the rim for a Duke 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (David Robinson chuckles as son gets awkward bounce on 3-pointer) 2020/03/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: David Robinson chuckles as son gets awkward bounce on 3-pointer

videos.description: Tre Jones throws up an alley-oop to Cassius Stanley who throws down a two-handed jam to cap the Duke fast break.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jones lobs to Stanley for fast break slam) 2020/03/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jones lobs to Stanley for fast break slam

videos.description: After Duke defeats NC State 88-69, Coach K runs by the first row of Cameron Crazies to hand out high-fives.
